OL,3,CNew 'pilot' nursery set up in Jersey
OL,5,FA new nursery will open for two to
OL,6,Fthree year olds with additional needs
OL,7,Fin Jersey.
OL,9,FStarting in October 2024, the pilot
OL,10,Fscheme at d'Auverge school in St
OL,11,FHelier, may lead to similar provisions
OL,12,Fopening within other Government
OL,13,Fprimary schools.
OL,15,FThe Education Minister, Deputy Rob
OL,16,FWard, said: "I'm delighted that we are
OL,17,Fable to offer this provision to
OL,18,Fparents and families in the coming
OL,19,Fweeks.
