OL,3,CNew 'pilot' nursery set up in Jersey
OL,5,F"It is the first step, and one of a
OL,6,Fnumber of possible options we're
OL,7,Flooking at to achieve the universal
OL,8,Foffer for 2 to 3 year olds".
OL,10,FThe headteacher of d'Auvergne, Sam
OL,11,FCooper, added: "We're very happy to
OL,12,Fsupport the pilot in any way we can.
OL,14,F"(We) look forward to welcoming more
OL,15,Fchildren into our wider school
OL,16,Fcommunity".
